children.text: The key to success is Faith....
You're in a forest, and the sun is setting slowly...
"I should get going," you say to yourself. "Mom won't be happy."
Does life ever feel like a mountain? Impossible to climb?
But just believe and you're halfway there.
But just believe and you're halfway there.

This is where you went sledging with friends all the time.... It used to be fun!
But just believe and you're halfway there.
But recently.... they haven't been inviting you.
But recently.... they haven't been inviting you.
But recently.... they haven't been inviting you.
But recently.... they haven't been inviting you.
It's okay, though, right? You can sledge by yourself.
You know this place. "Sandstone Ruins," you mutter. Your parents brought you here on your last holiday!
That was the last time you can remember where everyone in your family was happy.
